---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Index from "./index.astro";
import Guides from "./guides.astro";
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
import github from "./assets/github.jpg"
---

<Layout title="About Me">
    <main>
        <div>
            <h2><b>- About Me</b></h2>

            <p1><b>How I got into Astro</b></p1>
            <p>I like to mostly to create react apps! But I decided to try astro and now I love it. Altough it's only used for static webpages it's cool! For me its a lot like react too. So yep I like it!</p>
            <p>I am a 8 year old boy and I first got into react and astro. When I was a grade 3 but I failed so tried again and the did it! Now I can code basic webpages in react and astro and gatsby and vite and blah blah blah! A whole lot of other stuff!</p>

            <style>
                * {
                    background-color: blanchedalmond;
                    font-family: "Fredoka" 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif ;
                }
            
                main {
                    margin: auto;
                    padding: 1.5rem;
                    max-width: 60ch;
                }
                h1 {
                    font-size: 3rem;
                    font-weight: 800;
                    margin: 0;
                }
                .text-gradient {
                    background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
                    -webkit-background-clip: text;
                    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
                    background-size: 400%;
                    background-position: 0%;
                }
                .instructions {
                    line-height: 1.6;
                    margin: 1rem 0;
                    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent), 25%);
                    background-color: white;
                    padding: 1rem;
                    border-radius: 0.4rem;
                }
                .instructions code {
                    font-size: 0.875em;
                    font-weight: bold;
                    background: rgba(var(--accent), 12%);
                    color: rgb(var(--accent));
                    border-radius: 4px;
                    padding: 0.3em 0.45em;
                }
                .instructions strong {
                    color: rgb(var(--accent));
                }
                .link-card-grid {
                    display: grid;
                    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(24ch, 1fr));
                    gap: 1rem;
                    padding: 0;
                }
            </style> 
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>